&lt;li&gt;Support benchmarking, analysis, and performance optimization of various model architectures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to efforts in scaling out distributed model training under guidance and participate in discussions related to the co-design of Tenstorrent&#39;s hardware and software stack.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the integration of Tenstorrent software with widely used tools in the machine learning community.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
